{"tid":104838,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼婆「反共反上腦」：國語 是 共產黨 語言","createTime":"2017-02-02T11:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T02:34:45.000Z","uid":53060,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3966c4eb55ff9b1e68b482bed3c24b09df29e81f","tid":104838,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:58:41.000Z","msg":"]<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170123/280pix/1485170341_a784.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170123%2F280pix%2F1485170341_a784.jpg&h=b4e4352d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢叫甘茜蓮，係挪威人，亦係廣東話老師。對佢嚟講廣東話好重要，係守護香港嘅防線：「語言係文化嘅中心，如果冇語言，咁文化係乜嘢呀？」感恩香港有個甘老師為大家捍衛廣東話！<br />\n<br />\n中國人句話叫「黃皮白心」，形容徹底西化的華人。挪威人甘茜蓮卻剛剛相反&mdash;&mdash; 居港多年，早變得「白皮黃心」，甚至自發捍衛廣東話。「我很喜歡廣東話，好搞笑；<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">國語現在對我來說，是共產黨語言</span></span>，但廣東話是搞笑、飲啤酒、講笑的語言。」兼職粵語老師的阿茜個性率真，提到回歸後廣東話被邊緣化的問題，她一針見血：「香港唔係北京吖嘛﹗」"},{"pid":"c2656960675ee0be9b5c7dc9aa0109b6cf41f7dc","tid":104838,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:59:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170124&amp;guid=56213273&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170124%26guid%3D56213273%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=6d478e98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170124%26guid%3D56213273%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=4ccc28fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170124&amp;guid=56213273&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"2927e72560d513608dd90cfce8327de7e4d5d342","tid":104838,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:00:01.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"df8ca3366e0cf732c99749f5821911fc8808f787","tid":104838,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"在<span style=\"color: red;\">中華民國(台灣)，國語</span>是指由中華民國政府規範與管理的官方標準漢語，主要<span style=\"color: red;\">以北京官話為標準，文字則使用繁體中文</span>，一般通稱為國語、國文，主管機構為中華民國教育部[2]。"},{"pid":"392bfa6918015de06b71302ff5d52ea678ce5dca","tid":104838,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:02:21.000Z","msg":"反共反普通話都算<br />\n仲要反埋台灣國語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明兩種語言來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230967be9170c6184bf05ea45ea37cc2199a0727","tid":104838,"uid":57110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:03:58.000Z","msg":"佢咁講其實唔錯得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為今日嘅普通話其實係共産黨改過嘅北京話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cdd496540149a6381b69e6d05ba28d6a2dd956","tid":104838,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:05:36.000Z","msg":"國語「垃圾」：「l&egrave; s&egrave;」<br />\n普通話「垃圾」： 「lā jī」<br />\n<br />\n明明2種唔同語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0924a8890bb8a8408b3c58007c3a949e9cbdcd","tid":104838,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:06:28.000Z","msg":"冇錯啊"},{"pid":"acc3f952dc4465ffb7bd998d653d366628406f57","tid":104838,"uid":51859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國語「垃圾」：「l&egrave; s&egrave;」<br />\n普通話「垃圾」： 「lā jī」<br />\n<br />\n明明2種唔同語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台灣國民黨就是蘇共野種，推行國語是為了打壓台語文化和台灣民族。"},{"pid":"38dc54979af0003c7dea3dfd3ee88cd5658ef1e8","tid":104838,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國語「垃圾」：「l&egrave; s&egrave;」<br />\n普通話「垃圾」： 「lā jī」<br />\n<br />\n明明2種唔同語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個例子唔關事<br />\n本來係讀le se <br />\n但大陸班文盲有邊讀邊 <br />\n讀咗le ji"},{"pid":"fb2759e33ec1f11e883840026c0630745cdc017d","tid":104838,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國語「垃圾」：「l&egrave; s&egrave;」<br />\n普通話「垃圾」： 「lā jī」<br />\n<br />\n明明2種唔同語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實連台灣人都話國語係北京胡語！！！<br />\n<a href=\"http://taiwanwe.org/discuss01.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftaiwanwe.org%2Fdiscuss01.htm&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=941b8c11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://taiwanwe.org/discuss01.htm</a> <br />\n漢人未來台灣之前，整個台灣平地都是平埔族的天下，在漢人入侵的強勢文化與統治下，平埔族的語言、文化、人種全部消失無蹤。北京語（<span style=\"color: red;\">國語，應該稱為北京胡語較適合</span>）並非純漢語，在五胡亂華及元宋，胡族入侵的強大政治力量下，原來北方官話的漢語與胡語混合，形成入聲消失，簡化成四聲的變種語言──北京胡語。政治、教育及傳播媒體消滅台語的力量，在國民黨的掌控下，實在太恐怖了，台灣各族群的語言與文化，在國民黨外來政權的殖民地心態統治下，如不大力挽救，必然走上平埔族滅亡的命運。"},{"pid":"c3b14c078df2fd3acbfb77b1a9c9a7bdc4ff6019","tid":104838,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>國語「垃圾」：「l&egrave; s&egrave;」<br />\n普通話「垃圾」： 「lā jī」<br />\n<br />\n明明2種唔同語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個例子唔關事<br />\n本來係讀le se <br />\n但大陸班文盲有邊讀邊 <br />\n讀咗la  ji</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c49e86c38d00fdf1eb4a99dbe41c950c20417f80","tid":104838,"uid":24339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:12:01.000Z","msg":"國語=普通話<br />\n台狗=共狗<br />\n兩邊一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92b74c616593618be139308003b20f57da3cadf","ti